Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:04.44,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two people's deductions and suspense\Nfill the gulf between love and hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.15,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A strange case with lots of mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What will Conan, Heiji and Jodie do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:49.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hattori and I suspected that Jodie{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-sensei{\r\be10}\Nbelonged to the Black Organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so we went to Jodie's apartment to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:00.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, we encountered an unexpected incident\Nat the entrance of her apartment bulding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From above...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A man came falling from the twenty-first floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, was the front door locked when you got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It was locked up tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A locked-room mystery, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I say it's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we thought so too, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we went into Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,an' saw that curtain in the window, we changed our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain's pulled down an' the rail's bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A couple of hooks got pulled off too, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've grabbed the curtain as he was about to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would a guy trying to off himself do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then this wasn't a suicide, it was—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a murder case, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:20.56,Title,,0,0,0,,English Teacher vs. Great Detective of the West\N(Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's also a locked room murder,\Nlike we so often see in novels or movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apartment is right next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two just came to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just when we were leaving the building to go out for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came falling down in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? Have you solved this locked room murder mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think the strange mark on the window glass may have something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a mark like something hit it from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We developed the pictures that Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most are just shots of the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there was a picture with a strange figure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we blew it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he {\i1}was{\i0} grabbin' the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's throwing something into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's a cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that mark on the window\Nis from the phone bouncin' off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he throw his phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was a very annoying phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is police business! You civilians stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, talk about hot tempered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to help him but not anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with those guys.\NHow does this happen to me so often?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, although it's true that they may be annoying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for some reason, we solve\Na lot of cases with them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did the killer get Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nto throw himself out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could've done from outside\Nwas aim the flash at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was nothing strange about the mail that Nakamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could've said somethin' on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who'd jump out a window just\Nbecause somebody called and told him to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I wanna know is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why'd Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} try to throw\Nhis phone into the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking that he left a clue on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and didn't want it to fall and break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, lucky for us it {\i1}didn't{\i0} break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't find any clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.69,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.12,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What! Time! Is! It?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's 8:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna ask ya one more time, ya dummy!{Not straight, but it really works here =P}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}K-Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:45.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I totally forgot I was supposed to see Kazuha tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said that you\Nwanted to go try out that restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.48,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry, I'll have to take a raincheck on that...{usommie}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji! Where are ya now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.98,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're breakin' up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uh-oh... I've only got one bar!{prolly loose, but effective}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.82,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Heiji? Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I can't get to where you are from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... Tokyo, I'm in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.29,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was gonna get back to you as soon\Nas I finished what I had to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kinda excuse is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You told me to wait in front of\NBig Man in Umeda at 7:00 tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even made a memo of it!{"memo" is a keyword here...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The killer is that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? An experiment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we do exactly what the three suspects were doin'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell to his death from the twenty-first floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,maybe we can figure out this\Nlocked-room murder mystery easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was just taking photographs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had just sent a text message...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had just made a rude phone call to Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even know if it was murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, what's the harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to carry out the experiment,\Nwe're missing some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Missing some things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liquor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember. Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell asleep drunk\Nbefore he fell to his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who's going to play the role of the drunk victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the problem... We can't\Nhave a cop drinkin' booze on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm underage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the only person who could do it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can ya booze up an' play the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I am doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you have to get me my favorite kind of drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very, very delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happy to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel I can drink like a fish now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get everything set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it. Nakamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came back because you said you were doing an on-site investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come the foreign lady is getting drunk in Takai's bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to explain this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we're trying to reenact the crime as accurately as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're already done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. We put Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} in bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I placed my cell phone next to the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we reorganized the room a little bit without telling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you change the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll see when you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get this show on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:11:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, Nakamachi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent an e-mail to Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cell phone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I have to send an e-mail too... OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?{Typeset: "Who are you? (Kansaiben)" "Menu" "Back"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, teacher! Did you get my mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I got a lovely e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori... What kinda mail did you send her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next for the flashes of Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s camera
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as she took photos of the condo from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba, your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But will this experiment help us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to solve the mystery of the locked room murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't know 'til we try, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} made a call...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just make small talk for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What shall we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, now, how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the answer to the message I just sent ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the answer to the message I just sent ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, but first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me ask about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not just another boy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I'm just a regular high school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can't hear you clearly. Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's because we're so high in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It often happens when I use my cell phone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I get out on the balcony,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you should be hearing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a lot clearer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you, Mr. Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. We moved the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We knew she would move out onto the balcony
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to get better cell phone reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She assumed the window diagonal from the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was the one that opens onto the balcony,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it was actually the window with nothin' but air beneath it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, she almost fell just like Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were talkin' to Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}san{\r} on the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until the moment he fell, weren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Noboru Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bed is usually
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in front of the window facin' the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer moved the bed in front of the other window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he got the call on his cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} tried to go out of the window next to his bed as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bed was probably moved
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he was drinking with Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} excused himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,most likely saying that he was going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he snuck into Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and moved his bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was drunk and asleep in the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was carried to his bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the cell phone was placed right by the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that it was simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He called and said, "I can't hear ya!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But what if Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} had fallen because of this experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would've been fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see? Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tied a rope around her waist without telling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, all you have to do is explain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the police why you killed Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I'd do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if I really had meant to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I admit I was the one who moved the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takai asked me to help him rearrange his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never meant for him to get confused and fall. I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize what happened until you explained it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long, Takai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you see Hiraya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} in the world beyond, you can apologize to her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd confess over the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... You probably didn't know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} managed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to hang onto the curtain for a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before he fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pressed the voice memo button of his cell phone and recorded
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your words, which provided evidence that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you had the intention to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{UTB Your sad words of parting, saying that you were satisfied that}Ya just had to get in that parting shot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{UTB you had avenged the death of your dear girl, your junior in school.}when ya took revenge for the woman ya loved.{EOW}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your camera that you lent me a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry 'bout all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for acting as if you had been tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, it was so, so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell me your name, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I tell you my name, won't you tell me your true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to know why you pretend not being able to speak English
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even though you can speak very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we talked on the phone a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked you, "You're not just another boy, are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you answered, "Yes, I'm just another high school boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this case, "No, I'm just another boy" is right in Japanese,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but your answer was "Yes, I'm just another boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only a good speaker of English couid have answered the way you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you answered unconsciously in English to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since I'm an English-speaking foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My true identity is... an English teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, I wasn't pretending not to be able to speak English, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the silence worked better than your funnily disguised Japanese, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The grammar of your Japanese is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but your pronunciation is all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's obvious that you're just pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not being able to speak Japanese well
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to throw people off their guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can talk about that another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he knew that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't you think that the victim role player didn't need to actually get drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to carry out that experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like ya said, that teacher's pretty fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secretly snappin' photos of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and pretendin' she'd just gotten outta the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was wet, all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the hair dryer in the bathroom was still warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the body lotion spilled on the floor wasn't dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must've taken a bath earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,an' jumped back in the shower to buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was probably using that time to do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,something she didn't want us to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don'tcha worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took the film outta her camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, she's definitely hidin' somethin', but she don't seem like bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she don't look a thing like that American actress Chris Vineyard you're suspectin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing they got in common is their big jugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is that her true face?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What're ya sayin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why are you still here? Don't you have someone waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot about Kazuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, stay on your guard, Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealin' with a crook who robbed the Metropolitan Police Department!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gimme a call if ya find another suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll run right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie isn't my only suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two more people I've got to check out...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a remarkable boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Son of Heizo Hattori, chief of the Osaka Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Shin'ichi Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a private eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move this train! A man's been stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, please call the ticket control barriers connected to this platform,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:24:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ask them to check all the tickets from Tokyo Spirits and Noir Tokyo supporters trying to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop anyone who has a ticket bought before 5 PM from leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do it! If you don't, the killer might get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:16.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: The Hooligan Mystery\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Ticket
